library(dplyr)
boundary = 20
shrunk_factor = 0.05
dat <- tls@data
xy_filtered = dat %>% filter(dat$X > -boundary , dat$X < boundary,
                                   dat$Y > -boundary , dat$Y < boundary) 
      
small_dat = LAS(sample_n(xy_filtered , nrow(xy_filtered) * shrunk_factor ))
plot(small_dat)
